To use with VIM:

On regular platforms:
	Copy ftdetect/phdl.vim  to ~/.vim/ftdetect/
	Copy syntax/phdl.vim to ~/.vim/syntax/

On Microsoft Windows:
	Run ":echo $HOME" within vim to find Vim's idea of your home directory[1].
	Copy ftdetect/phdl.vim to $HOME/vimfiles/ftdetect/
	Copy syntax/phdl.vim to $HOME/vimfiles/syntax/
